Author: intertropical
Text: Broth, fruit (!!), vegetables, almond milk.   Please try to eat a little, friend :( you deserve to, no matter what. The ED can be a fucking trip, but I promise you that it will not make you gain any real weight or cause changes in your appearance. Sending love, take care.

Author: notalifeguard89
Text: Rice cakes, tuna, shrimp, veggies, broth. Even if you can't manage to get food down (please try), try to get some tea or a liquid calorie drink in. Please stay safe, it isn't worth it.
